data.description: Best of both worlds with gorgeous high end newly built house in an established neighborhood. Enjoy views of the city and mountains off the huge main level deck and a deck off the second floor master too! High end appliances in the gourmet kitchen with large island, hardwood floors and tile inset in the dining room. Bonus room upstairs even has great views! Lower level walkout daylight basement with family room plumbed for wet bar, 2 extra bedrooms, bath, utilityand a large storage room. Lovely tile work throughout! On demand hot water too!
